<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="rtl">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>نتيجة الثانويه العامه - 2024</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 16px;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        button {
            padding: 10px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background-color: #5cb85c;
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #4cae4c;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>ابحث برقم الجلوس او الاسم</h1>
        <form action="/search" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="query" placeholder="ادخل رقم جلوسك او اسمك..." required>
            <button type="submit">بحث</button>
        </form>
        <footer>
            &copy; 2024 <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100071043262787">حسين ناصر</a>. غير مسوؤل عن
            صحة
            النتيجه.
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>

</html>